    <briefdescription>
<para>Attach this script directly to: Detective Sheet Panel SETUP: </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Select &quot;Detective Sheet Panel&quot; in the Hierarchy.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Inspector → Add Component → <ref refid="class_detective_sheet_manager" kindref="compound">DetectiveSheetManager</ref>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Leave the sheetPanel field empty — it auto-assigns to this GameObject.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Drag &quot;Detective Button&quot; (inside Options Panel) into the detectiveButton slot.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>The panel will be hidden automatically on Play — no need to set it inactive. </para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
